      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The engine currently runs roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, while the transmission has started to slip during gear changes. Externally, the paint is faded with several noticeable dents and patches of surface rust beginning to form. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This is a project car best suited for someone with mechanical expertise or for use as a parts donor.",
