      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s reliable, super comfy, and totally ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me! It\u2019s in really great shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for a new home. I've priced it to move quickly because I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Swing by and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
