    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 Coupe. At its heart is the S54B32 naturally aspirated straight-six, featuring a high-pressure Double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential. This example has received extensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for exceptional kinematic feedback. While the exterior displays honest wear from spirited use, the drivetrain is dialed in, featuring a recently calibrated valve train and fresh fluids throughout. An ideal specimen for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
